@startuml
title GoF Pattern : Memento + Observer

note as GoFLabel
  **<<Memento + Observer>>**
end note

class Document {
  + content: String
  + save(): void
}
class Snapshot {
  + state: String
  + restore(): void
}
class DocumentController {
  + attachObserver(Observer observer): void
  +  detachObserver(Observer observer): void
}
interface Toolbar {
}
interface StatusBar {
}
interface PreviewPanel {
}

DocumentController --> Toolbar
DocumentController --> StatusBar
DocumentController --> PreviewPanel
Toolbar ..> Document
StatusBar ..> Document
PreviewPanel ..> Document
GoFLabel .. Document
@enduml